    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier as a complete record of the MRL 5 evaluation. The assessment transparently documents all 13 credibility factors, identifies 6 unassessed epistemic gaps, and records achieved levels below required levels for all 7 assessed factors. The package is accepted as a faithful and complete negative finding supporting the Not Accepted device submission decision.",
